 * Do not deploy as-is — swap `MOCK` for a live loader when the engine ships.
 *
 * Conventions matched:
 *   - StatsLayout shell + <StatsMasthead slot="mast">, same as /stats/skaters.
 *   - Table is the canonical HGBTable (via ProjectionsTable wrapper) — real
 *     sorting, conference chips filter, CSV/PNG export.
 *   - Canonical light team logos via teamLogoSrc (/logos/nhl/{abbr}_light.svg).
